    <item>
      <title>Lots of Vitamin D needed weekly during Breast Cancer Treatment (mean 20,000 IU up to 140,000 IU)</title>
      <link>http://localhost:1313/posts/lots-of-vitamin-d-needed-weekly-during-breast-cancer-treatment-mean-20000-iu-up-to-140000-iu/</link>
      <pubDate>Fri, 29 Mar 2024 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate>
      <guid>http://localhost:1313/posts/lots-of-vitamin-d-needed-weekly-during-breast-cancer-treatment-mean-20000-iu-up-to-140000-iu/</guid>
      <description>&lt;ul&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Personalized Vitamin D dosing&lt;/strong&gt; ranged from 2,000 IU to 140,000 weekly for Breast Cancer:&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;ul&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;A range of 70 to 1&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;/ul&gt;&#xA;&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;Treating healthy people typically requires a range of Vitamin D of only 4 to 1&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;The women getting Breast Cancer treatment  were clearly not uniformly unhealthy&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;/ul&gt;&#xA;&lt;blockquote&gt;&#xA;&lt;/blockquote&gt;&#xA;&lt;ul&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;The study failed to note improvement in outcomes vs women not getting Vitamin D&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;ul&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;Shorter treatment durations, less chemo used, less recurrence&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;/ul&gt;&#xA;&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;/ul&gt;&#xA;&lt;nav id=&#34;TableOfContents&#34;&gt;&#xA;  &lt;ul&gt;&#xA;    &lt;li&gt;&#xA;      &lt;ul&gt;&#xA;        &lt;li&gt;&#xA;          &lt;ul&gt;&#xA;            &lt;li&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;#course-of-vitamin-d-levels-in-newly-diagnosed-non-metastatic-breast-cancer-patients-over-one-year-with-quarterly-controls-and-substitution&#34;&gt;Course of Vitamin D Levels in Newly Diagnosed Non-Metastatic Breast Cancer Patients over One Year with Quarterly Controls and Substitution&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;            &lt;li&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;#vitamindwiki---a-hrefpostsvitamin-d-not-one-size-type-form-route-for-all-stylecolor-red-text-decoration-underline-titlethis-postcategory-does-not-exist-yet-vitamin-d-not-one-size-type-form-route-for-all---jan-2022vitamin-d-not-one-size-type-form-route-for-all---jan-2022a&#34;&gt;VitaminDWiki - &lt;a href=&#34;http://localhost:1313/posts/vitamin-d-not-one-size-type-form-route-for-all&#34; style=&#34;color: red; text-decoration: underline;&#34; title=&#34;This post/category does not exist yet: Vitamin D: not one size, type, form, route for all - Jan 2022&#34;&gt;Vitamin D: not one size, type, form, route for all - Jan 2022&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;            &lt;li&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;#vitamindwiki---a-hrefpostshuge-variation-in-response-to-vitamin-d-supplementation-personal-vitamin-d-response-index-stylecolor-red-text-decoration-underline-titlethis-postcategory-does-not-exist-yet-huge-variation-in-response-to-vitamin-d-supplementation--personal-vitamin-d-response-index--dec-2016huge-variation-in-response-to-vitamin-d-supplementation--personal-vitamin-d-response-index--dec-2016a&#34;&gt;VitaminDWiki - &lt;a href=&#34;http://localhost:1313/posts/huge-variation-in-response-to-vitamin-d-supplementation-personal-vitamin-d-response-index&#34; style=&#34;color: red; text-decoration: underline;&#34; title=&#34;This post/category does not exist yet: Huge variation in response to vitamin D supplementation – personal vitamin D response index – Dec 2016&#34;&gt;Huge variation in response to vitamin D supplementation – personal vitamin D response index – Dec 2016&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;            &lt;li&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;#vitamindwiki---personalized-treatment-of-vitamin-dpostspersonalized-treatment-of-vitamin-d&#34;&gt;VitaminDWiki - &lt;a href=&#34;http://localhost:1313/posts/personalized-treatment-of-vitamin-d&#34;&gt;Personalized treatment of Vitamin D&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;          &lt;/ul&gt;&#xA;        &lt;/li&gt;&#xA;      &lt;/ul&gt;&#xA;    &lt;/li&gt;&#xA;  &lt;/ul&gt;&#xA;&lt;/nav&gt;&#xA;&lt;hr&gt;&#xA;&lt;h4 id=&#34;course-of-vitamin-d-levels-in-newly-diagnosed-non-metastatic-breast-cancer-patients-over-one-year-with-quarterly-controls-and-substitution&#34;&gt;Course of Vitamin D Levels in Newly Diagnosed Non-Metastatic Breast Cancer Patients over One Year with Quarterly Controls and Substitution&lt;/h4&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;Nutrients. 2024 Mar 15;16(6):854. &lt;a href=&#34;https://doi.org/10.3390/nu16060854.&#34;&gt;doi: 10.3390/nu16060854.&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</description>
    </item>
